<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ideffdb1cb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7215"><num value="7215">§ 7215.</num><heading> Applicability of payment limitations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Sections 1308 through 1308–3 of this title shall be applicable to contract payments made under this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ideffdb1cc-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/127/tI/s115/a">Pub. L. 104–127, title I, § 115(a)</ref>, <date date="1996-04-04">Apr. 4, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/902">110 Stat. 902</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
